   FINANCE-HOOKER (Undated) _ My husband has just passed away and I
am wondering how to best invest my money. By Kenneth Hooker.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   OLY-MULLOY (Undated) _ Melissa Mulloy can hit the big shot in a
pressure situation. Her coach can always count on her to score.
That's why she's one of only three Americans who will compete in
the women's 50-meter three position sport rifle competition in
Sydney. By Michael Smith. 970 words.
</P>
<P>
   OLY-USGYMNASTS (St. Louis) _ For the US gymnasts, the road to
Sydney begins in the shadow of the Gateway Arch. By the time the
math and back-room politicking are done, six men and sixs women
will make the team. By John Powers. 715 words.
</P>
<P>
   BBO-RYAN-COLUMN (Undated) _ There will be a flood of tears when
the old Fenway finally closes. By Bob Ryan. 850 words.
</P>
