help him paint by cyber-committee. Under the ``brush-pseudonym''
Jessi Buchanan, Cohen recently launched ``Bid'N'Pick Art Project
2000,'' an interactive wacky artfest in which the e-mail bidders
call the shots and Cohen paints the canvas. (Kicklighter, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
