and hairy. This is because they spent lots of hours crouched in
bushes waiting for a mastodon or buffalo to come by, and it was in
the days before Gore-Tex. All about hairless beauty standards and
ways to wax, zip and lotion those follicles away. (Grand Junction)
</P>
