<SLUG> BC-VOTERS-AARP27-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AARP RELEASES POLL, PLANS VOTER EDUCATION CAMPAIGN
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
