<SLUG> BC-KEYRATES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
   c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   --------------------Wednesday---Tuesday--Year Ago
</P>
<P>
