 &HT;    
 &HT;    BERNARD GLADSTONE'S ``HOME IMPROVEMENT QUESTIONS AND ANSWERS''
for Sun., Aug. 13, 2000, which included:
 &HT;    _The magic trick to stop cold water pipes from sweating: foam
