<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST-LEADERS (Jerusalem) _ Arriving back home, Mideast
leaders Yasser Arafat and Ehud Barak seek vital support to push
negotiations _ Arafat with Egypt's Hosni Mubarak and Barak with old
warrior Ariel Sharon. By Charles M. Sennott. 1100 words.
</P>
<P>
   CONCORDE-GRIEF (Paris) _ The outpouring of grief in France in
the aftermath of the Concorde crash shows the strong bonds that
have been created between the French and Germans since World War
II. By Kevin Cullen. 1000 words.
