<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-26 20:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3972 &Cx1f; tta-z
u i BC-MIDEAST-TALKS-1050(2T     07-26 1076
