 &UR; MEDIABYTES (COLUMN) _  &LR; Although his stentorian voice and pointy
eyebrows made him a political reporting legend, Sam Donaldson won't
be on television during the approaching party conventions. The
66-year-old newsman will be online.
</P>
<P>
   There's no more enthusiastic _ or more unlikely _ dot-commer
than Donaldson, who will Webcast two interviews a day from
Philadelphia and Los Angeles, where Republicans and Democrats
convene next week and next month, respectively.  &UR; COLUMN BY DAN &LR; 
 &UR; FOST &LR;
</P>
